column5: i don't agree with the thunderstorms but girl the coffee i'm right there with you

i'm right there feeling the same as you. i'd like to think when i go there will be peace with those i love to help them understand the hurt behind it. although they may never fully understand, just letting them know it's what happens to be the best for you. how can anyone say they know better if they aren't you? they can't.
i need that too i'm just sitting here hoping someone will find me i'm so sorry
